dc_title_s: Roads and ROW Waupaca County, WI 2023
dc_description_s: This data represents roads and Right Of Ways (ROW) for Waupaca County, Wisconsin in 2023 and includes the layers 'Waupaca_Roads_2023' and 'Waupaca_ROW_2023'. [Roads: This data represents the Waupaca County transportation network. A single line is used to represent the center of a road. All roads are geocoded with a address range.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most current data for this county, please visit: https://data2017-04-05t135915451z-waupacacounty.opendata.arcgis.com/
